          "end": 135
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "周書曰毋為虎傅翼將飛入邑擇人而食之",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 28
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "淮南王安曰天子之兵有征而無戰言莫敢校也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-22",
        "range": {
